entries.femaleVariant: Little shit who was here yesterday!
Dunno. I'm here today. This is mysterious, I do admit.
Lemme guess. Got yourself some shards yesterday, magic ones, amazing price?
Mh. Crap, trash, dickspittle – run out of words to describe how useless they are.
Well, you're not the first to get reamed, sir. These kids, they crawl outta nowhere, sell this shit left and right, then disappear back where they came from.
Lesson learned? Buy only from licensed, trusted traders. Like yours truly.
Those prices are an assurance, a guarantee of customer satisfaction. Interested in taking a look?
Startin' to think all you guys are in on this…
